org.pac4j.core.profile
Class UserProfile

java.lang.Object
  org.pac4j.core.profile.UserProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommonProfile
public class UserProfile
extends Object
implements Serializable

This class is the user profile retrieved from a provider after successful authentication : it's an identifier (string) and attributes (objects). The attributes definition is null (generic profile), it must be defined in subclasses.

Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Jerome Leleu
